Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined his arms could still move \Non their own after being detached!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I threw the explosive tags?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hid in the smoke long enough to send his right arm underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a true blue Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their abilities are all out of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said we were finished, but you still had no idea what I was capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was better to keep your distance as you played your next hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually think, unlike my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Chouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikudan Hari Sensha{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:04.70,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Nikudan Hari Sensha: Spiked Meat Tank)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My god...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like Naruto's taken a single break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't think so. He has to perfect his new technique as soon as possible, if we're going to be sent as Kakashi-sensei's backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time limit's twenty-four hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a difficult situation, but all we can do is believe in Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:02:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're the only team who can \Nwork smoothly with Kakashi-sensei's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:07.22,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,mijika ni arumono
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:07.22,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be extra careful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.55,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,tsune ni ki wo tsuketeinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.55,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,with the things nearest to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:13.47,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,amari ni chikasugite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:13.47,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:16.44,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,miushinatteshimaisou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:16.44,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.99,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,anata ga saikin taiken shita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.99,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain to me this happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.91,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,shiawase wa ittai nan desu ka{\b1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.91,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,that you just got to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.74,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,megumaresugeteite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.74,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you're so blessed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.57,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,omoidasenai kamo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.57,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can't even remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.46,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,ima koko ni iru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.46,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,That you stand here now
