Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:40.29,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,That you live and breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:43.34,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,tada sore dake no koto ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:43.34,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all little miracles
