Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.72,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be extra careful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.85,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,tsune ni ki wo tsuketeinai to
