Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.76,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.43,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,miushinatteshimaisou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.43,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:59.81,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.31,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:05.03,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll never take it for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.82,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,oitsuzuketekita yume
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.82,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine to say "Never give up."
