Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.63,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,and with its help, survive another day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:25.59,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll never take it for granted
