Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to be wary of Sasuke's fire element.
