Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we need someone to take care of Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll use my Mind-Body Switch technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you go, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he even scratches you with an attack and gets your blood, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle him all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And fulfill {\i1}that{\i0} role as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:04.80,NextEpTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(470,0)\pos(817,500)}The Terrifying Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Terrifying Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai-kun, what are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? You're not very energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A burning vigor is what makes the youth young! And you're lacking passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to give you a very special item as a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gorgeous suit is specially made so it breathes, \Nis durable, and always fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect bodysuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I wear one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a highly sought-after item and is hard to get your hands on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these beautiful body lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee that if you wear it during training once, \Nyou'll never be able to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly a miracle gown for all youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle gown?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just between the two of us, this suit has made \Nboth Naruto and Lee power up big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened. So how does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be blunt, gay.
